video.title: CSI: NY
video.synopsis: Science in the service of crime fighting comes to the Big Apple in the second spinoff of the popular "CSI" franchise.

episodes.synopsis: Detective Mac Taylor discovers the body of a woman in Brooklyn Heights, when his investigation leads him to a serial killer.
episodes.title: Blink

episodes.synopsis: Detectives Stella Bonasera and Danny Messer's mission to find a brutal rapist is hindered, as the victim has no memory of the assault.
episodes.title: Creatures Of The Night

episodes.synopsis: A practical joke spirals into a century spanning murder mystery when a skeleton placed on a tour bus turns out to be authentic.
episodes.title: American Dreamers

episodes.synopsis: CSI detectives investigate when New York's hottest DJ is found dead minutes before being crowned the undisputed "scratching" champion.
episodes.title: Grand Master

episodes.synopsis: Detective Mac Taylor and Danny Messer go underground, entering the world of the 'Sandhogs,' men who burrow beneath New York City.
episodes.title: A Man A Mile

episodes.synopsis: In a test of faith, Mac Taylor assigns Detectives Danny Messer and Aiden Burn to one of the CSI team's toughest cases yet.
episodes.title: Outside Man

episodes.synopsis: A Chinatown robbery goes south when one security guard is killed and the other mistakenly fires shots at a gas tank, burning two of the robbers alive.
episodes.title: Rain

episodes.synopsis: Panic ensues at the New York Mercantile Exchange when a briefcase is left behind, it is traced back to a stockbroker who mysteriously disappeared.
episodes.title: Three Generations Are Enough

episodes.synopsis: When a mounted New York City police officer is shot off his horse, Detective Mac Taylor and the team comb the city for suspects.
episodes.title: Officer Blue

episodes.synopsis: The brutal stabbing of a young woman leads Detectives Mac Taylor and Stella Bonasera to Stuyvesant Town, the middle-class epicenter of New York City.
episodes.title: Night, Mother

episodes.synopsis: The electrocution of a young man on the third rail of the subway leads into the world of an extreme sport where taking risks is part of the game.
episodes.title: Tri-Borough

episodes.synopsis: Competitive dog owners become the prime suspects in a murder investigation when Detective Mac Taylor examines the death of a dog trainer.
episodes.title: Recycling

episodes.synopsis: The investigation of a suburban kid found beaten to death in Van Cortland Park leads the CSI team to Tanglewood, home to a group of wannabe gangsters.
episodes.title: Tanglewood

episodes.synopsis: Detectives Mac Taylor and Stella Bonasera uncover the body of a teenaged boy crammed into a 2' x 2' x 2' box buried in the sand at Coney Island.
episodes.title: Blood, Sweat And Tears

episodes.synopsis: Detectives Mac Taylor and Danny Messer find themselves on the trail of an elusive killer when an expectant bride drops dead on her wedding day.
episodes.title: 'Til Death Do We Part

episodes.synopsis: While investigating a truck-jacking, Detectives Mac Taylor and Stella Bonasera uncover a body pancaked underneath ten tons of steel.
episodes.title: Hush

episodes.synopsis: When young gang members murder the owner of an upscale Bronx wine store, the CSIs must work to find evidence that ties someone to the crime.
episodes.title: The Fall

episodes.synopsis: A celebration for the release of a report on police corruption ends in bloodshed, when shots ring out on the 65th floor of a Midtown high rise.
episodes.title: The Dove Commission

episodes.synopsis: Detective Mac Taylor and Stella Bonasera discover a dead woman among the dirty sheets at an industrial laundry facility.
episodes.title: Crimes And Misdemeanors

episodes.synopsis: The home invasion murder of a college student sends Detectives on the trail of China White, uncut heroin that has fallen into the wrong hands.
episodes.title: Supply And Demand

episodes.synopsis: An armed suspect is uncovered at a secured crime scene. The routine investigation becomes a foot pursuit through the subway tunnels of New York City.
episodes.title: On The Job

episodes.synopsis: Detectives discover the investigation of a vehicular homicide victim collides with a Boston baseball fan found dead in a parking lot.
episodes.title: The Closer

episodes.synopsis: When a casual breakfast turns into a shootout, Detective Mac Taylor must put the pieces of the crime back together again.
episodes.title: What You See Is What You See

episodes.synopsis: It's summer in the city as Mac and Hawkes investigate the suspicious death of a free climber attempting to scale the Empire State Building.
episodes.title: Summer In The City

episodes.synopsis: Stella and Danny investigate why a young, beautiful and blind woman was left strangled on a rooftop. Did cuddle parties have anything to do with it?
episodes.title: Grand Murder At Central Station

episodes.synopsis: It's mayhem at the Bronx Zoo. Mac, Danny and new CSI Lindsay Hamilton look into the death of a man thrown to the tigers.
episodes.title: Zoo York

episodes.synopsis: A man found beaten to death at the San Gennaro festival leads Mac and Stella from the alleys of Mott Street to the power players of Wall Street.
episodes.title: Corporate Warriors

episodes.synopsis: Mac, Stella and Lindsay discover why a young dancer with a winning lottery ticket in her pocket was thrown from the Roosevelt Bridge Island Tram.
episodes.title: Dancing With The Fishes

episodes.synopsis: The witness to a brutal elevator slaying has disappeared, and as the CSIs track her down they uncover the world of Manhattan "Lolitas".
episodes.title: Youngblood

episodes.synopsis: Detective Mac Taylor and CSI Miami Lieutenant Horatio Caine follow the evidence from steamy Miami to steely New York as they close in on Henry Darius.
episodes.title: Manhattan Manhunt

episodes.synopsis: When murder comes to play at a high-stakes poker game, the CSIs work to find out why what they thought was a cheater's revenge was misidentification.
episodes.title: Bad Beat

episodes.synopsis: In a New York doll "hospital", Mac and Danny recover the corpse of the doll "doctor" beneath hundreds of body parts - doll body parts.
episodes.title: City Of The Dolls

episodes.synopsis: A rising roller derby star drops dead in the middle of a bout, and Mac and Stella come to the rink to investigate the death.
episodes.title: Jamalot

episodes.synopsis: A billionaire is found dead in his bedroom, when Danny begins to process the scene he trips a panic button, sealing himself in with the victim.
episodes.title: Trapped

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate the death of two models at New York City's hottest fashion show - where all of the clothes consist of nothing but body paint.
episodes.title: Wasted

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate a prank gone bad when a "subway surfer" met with the ultimate wipeout, but soon understand that the death was no accident.
episodes.title: Risk

episodes.synopsis: Stella thinks she has finally caught a night off, but the host of a private art show she's attending is skewered with a high tech bow and arrow.
episodes.title: Stuck On You

episodes.synopsis: Stella and Mac examine a case in which a man was shot to death as a result of one of New York City's dangerous water gun wars.
episodes.title: Fare Game

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is found dead in her apartment building's water tower, Mac and Lindsay must team up to find who her killer was.
episodes.title: Cool Hunter

episodes.synopsis: When Mac and Stella discover a female corpse being devoured by beetles at a museum, they search for the villain behind the gruesome crime.
episodes.title: Necrophlia Americana

episodes.synopsis: Mac, Danny and Flack investigate the death of a medical intern and an illegal organ trafficking ring at New York hospital.
episodes.title: Live Or Let Die

episodes.synopsis: A patient from a mental hospital, who dresses as Superman, is found dead in an alleyway. The CSIs retrace his steps to restore justice to the city.
episodes.title: Super Men

episodes.synopsis: When an anonymous caller tells Mac there is a dead body buried at Giant's Stadium, evidence found at the scene points to one of the CSIs.
episodes.title: Run Silent, Run Deep

episodes.synopsis: The team investigates the murder of a limo driver at a Kid Rock concert. With Kid as a leading suspect, the CSIs find themselves backstage.
episodes.title: All Access

episodes.synopsis: A young woman, dressed as a mermaid, is discovered floating in a bed of kelp. The CSIs search Manhattan for her murderer.
episodes.title: Stealing Home

episodes.synopsis: A marine is found dead in Central Park. Across town, the team investigates the death of a woman found in a burned out car.
episodes.title: Heroes

episodes.synopsis: When a security guard is stabbed to death, Mac and Flack rush to the scene. While investigating the murder, a bomb is detonated.
episodes.title: Charge Of This Post

episodes.synopsis: When two bungee jumpers witness a death on the Brooklyn Bridge, Mac and his new love interest Peyton Driscoll are called in to investigate.
episodes.title: People with Money

episodes.synopsis: When Holly Golightly look-alikes rob a jewelry store the detectives find themselves questioning the girls' involvement in the world of blood diamonds.
episodes.title: Not What It Looks Like

episodes.synopsis: Danny and Lindsay investigate the death of a vodka spokeswoman dressed as an ice queen, and murdered with her scepter at a promotional event.
episodes.title: Love Run Cold

episodes.synopsis: A serial murderer leaves his victims in coded t-shirts. The team struggles to decode his mythological clues and put their main suspect behind bars.
episodes.title: Hung Out to Dry

episodes.synopsis: Danny and Lindsay explore the worlds of goth and glam when a young girl that belongs to the underground "suicide girls" cult is found dead.
episodes.title: Oedipus Hex

episodes.synopsis: A young hotel employee falls to her death from a hotel rooftop after she becomes embroiled in a deal with a scheming top model.
episodes.title: Open and Shut

episodes.synopsis: Mac is summoned from a night at the opera to a bloody crime scene. Across town, a famous bachelor is found dead in his swim gym.
episodes.title: Murder Sings the Blues

episodes.synopsis: When a paintball player is found shot to death, Flack realizes that a dirty cop under his supervision could be to blame.
episodes.title: Consequences

episodes.synopsis: After a night of heavy partying two underage girls make the reckless decision to drive home. In route, the girls get into an accident.
episodes.title: And Here's to You, Mrs. Azrael

episodes.synopsis: Mac and Flack investigate the death of parachute professional whose chute was pelted with dead pigeons causing him to plummet to the ground.
episodes.title: Sweet 16

episodes.synopsis: When Hawkes is framed for shooting a bartender and then later sent to prison, the team takes to the street to set their investigator free.
episodes.title: Raising Shane

episodes.synopsis: Mac and Stella work with a deaf family to find their daughter's killer. The team investigates the murder of a young skating sensation.
episodes.title: Silent Night

episodes.synopsis: When a rich real estate agent is found dead in a brownstone, Mac and Stella work with evidence that suggests he was either a kidnapper or kidnapee.
episodes.title: Obsession

episodes.synopsis: Danny and Mac find a corpse in a salt truck which is then later identified to be a high-powered extreme sports executive.
episodes.title: The Lying Game

episodes.synopsis: When a college student is found dead in a maze at the Queen's county farm museum, the CSIs discover a cult-like fraternity with harsh punishments.
episodes.title: Some Buried Bones

episodes.synopsis: Mac investigates the death of a girl found in a bathtub filled with rose petals. Stella questions the death of a man who fell in his fish tank.
episodes.title: Heart of Glass

episodes.synopsis: Mac and Danny investigate a case in which a delusional ex-con is found dead in his home while lying on top of a bed of cash.
episodes.title: The Ride-In

episodes.synopsis: The team investigates a case in which magic-trick inspired murders occur including a woman being cut in half while in a wooden box.
episodes.title: Sleight Out of Hand

episodes.synopsis: Danny and Lindsay find popular chef Alec Green dead in the wine cellar of his trendy restaurant with a corkscrew dangling from his chest.
episodes.title: A Daze of Wine and Roaches

episodes.synopsis: A knight in shining armor impaled with a lance in central park and a business man stabbed by an ice pick in a nearby hotel share a connection.
episodes.title: What Schemes May Come

episodes.synopsis: A serial killer's verdict is overturned when Mac jails his arresting officer, but a victim surfaces sporting the killer's signature.
episodes.title: Past Imperfect

episodes.synopsis: Stella is forced to deal with painful memories when Det. Valens visits and says her DNA is connected to a Philadelphia cold case making her a suspect.
episodes.title: Cold Reveal

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs are puzzled when evidence and witnesses point to John McEnroe as their murder suspect despite his air-tight alibi.
episodes.title: ...Comes Around

episodes.synopsis: Mac, Stella and Hawkes are forced to save the lab when a drug lord and his crew descend upon the CSI's vault to retrieve their merchandise.
episodes.title: Snow Day

episodes.synopsis: A murder on the Statue of Liberty rattles New York City as the CSI team tries to catch the killer before he strikes again.
episodes.title: Can You Hear Me Now?

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates the death of a professional diver in relation to a rumor of sunken treasure in the New York Harbor.
episodes.title: The Deep

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates a murder tied into a string of "spy" robberies targeting the elite while Mac continues to receive mysterious phone calls.
episodes.title: You Only Die Once

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York based team investigates the bizarre murder of a scientist, as well as the unusual death of a college girl.
episodes.title: Time's Up

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates a string of murders in New York that revolve around an online world, apparently performed by a hit man.
episodes.title: Down the Rabbit Hole

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate two eerie murders on Halloween; one, an apparent zombie attack, the other a faked murder/suicide in a house with a spooky past.
episodes.title: Boo

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team works to solve two seemingly unrelated murders that after investigations are underway turn out to be connected.
episodes.title: Commuted Sentences

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates crimes: one involving a model that was killed on a billboard in Times Square, and another centered around a robbery.
episodes.title: Buzzkill

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates the murder of a groom on his wedding day and the appearance of a mysterious box on the hood of Stella's car.
episodes.title: One Wedding and a Funeral

episodes.synopsis: Mac travels to Chicago in order to solve the mystery of the 333 caller while the rest of the CSI team works on a murder in a subway car.
episodes.title: The Thing About Heroes...

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates the death of a wealthy man in a hip nightclub and the inadvertent shooting of a young boy during a robbery.
episodes.title: Child's Play

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates the murder of the owner of a posh hotel as well as the death of a teenager that seems to be connected to Peter Pan.
episodes.title: Happily Never After

episodes.synopsis: After a young woman and a prominent judge are murdered, the CSI team works to discover the connection between the two crimes.
episodes.title: All in the Family

episodes.synopsis: The CSI team investigates the death of a street luger and the mysterious drowning of a woman in a self-sanitizing pay bathroom.
episodes.title: Playing with Matches

episodes.synopsis: When a trained female assassin comes to New York City, she really puts the CSI New York team members' abilities to the test.
episodes.title: DOA for a Day

episodes.synopsis: The kidnapping of a little girl and a fire set to her apartment building leaves CSI New York team member Stella feeling guilty and homeless.
episodes.title: Right Next Door

episodes.synopsis: A shark washes up on shore unloading a dead body and a bizarre crime scene that leaves the CSI New York team more than puzzled.
episodes.title: Like Water for Murder

episodes.synopsis: A high school dance is interrupted by the killing of the school's guidance counselor. Meanwhile, the taxi cab serial killer is still on the loose.
episodes.title: Admissions

episodes.synopsis: A professional basketball game ends early after a fan is chosen for the million dollar half court shot where he makes it and inexpediently dies.
episodes.title: Personal Foul

episodes.synopsis: The taxi cab killer whom the CSI New York team has been trying to catch strikes again, only this time it's at the expense of a New Jersey cop.
episodes.title: Taxi

episodes.synopsis: A bank robbery has Mac doing crime investigation from inside to help the robber prove he didn't kill one of the hostages.
episodes.title: Hostage

episodes.synopsis: The bank robbery saga from last season continues as Mac seeks revenge after nearly being killed by the mysterious "Joe".
episodes.title: Veritas

episodes.synopsis: A free street concert quickly turns into a crime scene, the victim in this case has been mysteriously plagued with radiation.
episodes.title: Page Turner

episodes.synopsis: Mac is traveling to Washington to testify in court until he realizes he's in the vicinity of a murder when a stewardess finds a dead body.
episodes.title: Turbulence

episodes.synopsis: A very powerful woman in the world of politics is found dead leaving many desperate in hoping that her information does not get leaked out.
episodes.title: Sex, Lies and Silicone

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate the death of a young archaeologist who may have unearthed the answer to one of New York City's oldest murder mysteries.
episodes.title: The Cost of Living

episodes.synopsis: When three defendants are gunned down on the eve of their trial, Mac is forced to make good on a promise he made to a reluctant witness.
episodes.title: Enough

episodes.synopsis: Investigation of a floating crime scene leads the team into the world of "SecretU" an art-house world of true confessionals.
episodes.title: Dead Inside

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team tackles their most unusual case yet: two murder victims within two weeks, both named 'Mac Taylor'.
episodes.title: My Name Is Mac Taylor

episodes.synopsis: When an unidentified body is discovered inside a crushed car, the CSIs must extract the bones in order to identify the victim and catch a predator.
episodes.title: The Box

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs are forced to investigate two crimes at once with a mysterious energy field near The Empire State Building at the center of both.
episodes.title: The Triangle

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs appear to have an open and shut case after a murder suspect is impaled during a police pursuit, but it turns out to only be the beginning.
episodes.title: Forbidden Fruit

episodes.synopsis: Young brides-to-be fight over a killer dress at the biggest wedding gown sale of the year and one of the shoppers winds up dead.
episodes.title: Help

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs must piece together a human jigsaw puzzle when a beloved wrestling coach's severed body parts are found buried throughout the city.
episodes.title: Rush to Judgment

episodes.synopsis: A Russian tourist is found stabbed to death and the CSIs come face to face with the frightening realities of human trafficking.
episodes.title: She's Not There

episodes.synopsis: When the Mayor's dead body falls from the ceiling at a charity fundraiser, Stella and her date find themselves in the middle of the crime scene.
episodes.title: The Party's Over

episodes.synopsis: When a buzzard flying over Manhattan drops a human eyeball from its claw, the race is on to find the body it belongs to.
episodes.title: No Good Deed

episodes.synopsis: A lethal pipe-bomb blows a Manhattan townhouse and valuable evidence to pieces, forcing the CSIs to get creative in reconstructing evidence.
episodes.title: Green Piece

episodes.synopsis: A former medical examiner is found murdered, a white powder found at the scene provides the CSIs with a major lead in tracking the killer.
episodes.title: Point of No Return

episodes.synopsis: When a Native American chief is shot, the CSIs struggle to translate which one of the several foreign suspects may have caused his death.
episodes.title: Communication Breakdown

episodes.synopsis: While investigating the shooting of a man in an empty theater, Stella realizes that the crime scene is oddly familiar and staged.
episodes.title: Prey

episodes.synopsis: When a man falls 52 stories to his death, and his body goes missing after it hits the ground, the CSIs must treat this as a missing persons case.
episodes.title: The Past, Present and Murder

episodes.synopsis: The most exclusive jewelry auction of the year ends abruptly when an appraiser is killed during the event. The investigation takes an emotional turn.
episodes.title: Yahrzeit

episodes.synopsis: Mac informs an ex-con that he served time for a crime he didn't commit, and Anna tells Danny "it's time" for the first CSI baby to be born.
episodes.title: Greater Good

episodes.synopsis: Stella discovers that New Yorkers are being murdered over ancient Greek artifacts, she hands over her badge to follow a clue that leads to Greece.
episodes.title: Grounds for Deception

episodes.synopsis: When transferring Robert Dunbrook's son from prison to court, the NYPD is ambushed by a group of professional kidnappers.
episodes.title: Pay Up

episodes.synopsis: One CSI New York team member's life is changed forever in a significant way following the aftermath of a shooting incident.
episodes.title: Epilogue

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team is tracking a cyber-killer who is currently threatening the lives of several medical healthcare workers.
episodes.title: Blacklist (Featuring Gravedigger)

episodes.synopsis: This week the CSI New York team is hunting for a serial killer who is equipped with an incredibly deadly sense of direction.
episodes.title: Lat 40 Degrees 47' N/Long 73 Degrees 58' W

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators discovers DNA which contradicts a murder case which was seemingly open and shut before.
episodes.title: Dead Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators is called in to investigate the very recent murder of an underground hip-hop dancer.
episodes.title: Battle Scars

episodes.synopsis: While investigating the murder of a software executive, the CSIs are exposed to the underground world of food splooshing.
episodes.title: It Happened To Me

episodes.synopsis: Las Vegas CSI Ray Langston comes to New York to help Mac and the CSI team try and save a hostage from a human trafficking ring.
episodes.title: Hammer Down (Crossover)

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators resumes their hunt for the Compass Killer after a body falls from the 59th street bridge.
episodes.title: Cuckoo'S Next

episodes.synopsis: In the culmination of a multi-episode mystery, the CSI New York team of investigators uncovers the dark lair of the Compass Killer.
episodes.title: Manhattanhenge

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team follows up on a 911 call to a vacant penthouse but find a nearly 100-Year-Old corpse and a booby-trapped house.
episodes.title: Death House

episodes.synopsis: A reformed drug addict is found dead in an alley and the CSI New York team discovers he was the victim of a premeditated plot.
episodes.title: Second Chances

episodes.synopsis: When the CSIs investigate a brutal stabbing, they discover that evidence at the crime scene was planted which pits them against a trusted colleague.
episodes.title: Criminal Justice

episodes.synopsis: When a beautiful star quarterback of the lingerie league is found murdered in a hot tub, the CSIs are called in to find out who wanted her dead.
episodes.title: Flag On The Play

episodes.synopsis: When a young woman is found dead in Central Park the CSI New York team is lured into the mysterious sub culture of vampirism.
episodes.title: Sanguine Love

episodes.synopsis: When a car racing legend dies in a fiery explosion, the CSI New York team of investigators discover that car tampering is the cause.
episodes.title: The Formula

episodes.synopsis: When four victims are found dead in a hotel room and the main suspect turns up wielding an axe, the CSIs try to piece together the details.
episodes.title: Uncertainty Rules

episodes.synopsis: When two young journalists are found dead on the eve of St. Patrick's Day, the CSIs try to find the clue at the end of the rainbow.
episodes.title: Pot Of Gold

episodes.synopsis: When a woman is found dead, the evidence and autopsy both suggest a suicide, but Stella is unconvinced and risks her life to pursue the case.
episodes.title: Rest In Peace, Marina Garito

episodes.synopsis: A death row inmate's final request brings hawkes to a Pennsylvania prison and face-to-face with a personal secret just as a prison riot erupts.
episodes.title: Redemption

episodes.synopsis: The shooting of a 14-year-old boy in front of his 12-year-old brother takes Detective Mac Taylor's drive for justice to another level.
episodes.title: Unusual Suspects

episodes.synopsis: When a slab of concrete starts bleeding in midtown, the CSIs' investigation takes them into an underground world of hardcore fighting.
episodes.title: Tales From The Undercard

episodes.synopsis: After being injured, Mac watches his neighbors while recuperating and witnesses mysterious activity that leads to murder.
episodes.title: Point Of View

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators follows a trail left by Shane Casey and realizes he is targeting a vacationing Danny out of revenge.
episodes.title: Vacation Getaway

episodes.synopsis: The newest CSI New York team of investigators' team member is welcomed by stumbling upon a woman murdered in the NYPD crime lab building.
episodes.title: The 34th Floor

episodes.synopsis: When a young woman appears to be strangled while in a live online chat that Adam witnesses the CSIs must determine if it was real or a hoax.
episodes.title: Unfriendly Chat

episodes.synopsis: When a couple is found beaten in their home, the CSIs think they have the suspect after a mother IDs her son, but all is not what it seems.
episodes.title: Damned If You Do

episodes.synopsis: When a powerful gang leader is murdered, the CSI New York team of investigators must find the killer before a street war breaks out.
episodes.title: Sangre Por Sangre

episodes.synopsis: A jewel heist at the penthouse of one of New York's most powerful attorneys takes a bizarre turn as the case leads the CSIs to a man in the morgue.
episodes.title: Out Of The Sky

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators finds a body on a rooftop and must find the killer who is manipulating crime scenes.
episodes.title: Do Not Pass Go

episodes.synopsis: With a sniper loose in New York City, Mac must relive an abduction case that might have created one of the city's deadliest foes.
episodes.title: Hide Sight

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators experience eerie occurrences after a woman is found who has literally been scared to death.
episodes.title: Scared Stiff

episodes.synopsis: Mac goes up against the deputy chief of detectives when a dark secret from the chief's past threatens his reputation and family.
episodes.title: Justified

episodes.synopsis: Mac and the CSI New York team search for the killer of a department store manager found dead in a holiday display window.
episodes.title: Shop Till You Drop

episodes.synopsis: When a man in full clown costume shoots a bakery owner, the CSIs investigate and discover a decision from Flack's past that may put him in jeopardy.
episodes.title: To What End

episodes.synopsis: When a Spanish club promoter is found dead, Detective Mac Taylor must battle with the head of Barcelona's crime lab to solve the case.
episodes.title: Holding Cell

episodes.synopsis: When a tractor-trailer carrying party guests mysteriously ends up at the bottom of the Hudson River, the CSIs must exhume the soggy remains.
episodes.title: Party Down

episodes.synopsis: When the CSIs track down a suave and charming hitman, their investigation uncovers a conspiracy with far-reaching implications.
episodes.title: Smooth Criminal

episodes.synopsis: When a serial rapist is murdered, restrained in the same manner as his victims, the CSIs weigh a feeling of justice against their sense of duty.
episodes.title: Vigilante

episodes.synopsis: When a conspiracy-obsessed woman is found dead, the CSIs investigate and discover that some of her theories may have had some truth to them.
episodes.title: The Untouchable

episodes.synopsis: When a popular student at Manhattan's most elite private school is murdered, the CSIs find themselves in the competitive world of the over privileged.
episodes.title: Do Or Die

episodes.synopsis: Jo balances personal and professional challenges when her adopted daughter, Ellie, is the key witness in a murder investigation.
episodes.title: Identity Crisis

episodes.synopsis: The team enters the competitive world of gourmet food trucks when one explodes at a SoHo food festival while Hawkes is there with his girlfriend.
episodes.title: Food For Thought

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate a woman's death as the work of a serial killer. Mac reconnects with his first partner after an ex-con begins stalking him.
episodes.title: Nothing For Something

episodes.synopsis: After a hail of gunfire tears through the crime lab, Mac and his ex-partner become part of a vendetta 17 years in the making.
episodes.title: Life Sentence

episodes.synopsis: Following a near-death experience, Detective Mac Taylor becomes quite determined to close his last remaining unsolved case.
episodes.title: Exit Strategy

episodes.synopsis: On the 10th anniversary of 9/11, Mac and the team remember specific moments from that day that were indelibly burned in their mind.
episodes.title: Indelible

episodes.synopsis: When an awkward teen is found dead, the team discovers that his efforts to win a sexy punk rock chick's heart may have gone a step too far.
episodes.title: Keep It Real

episodes.synopsis: When the body of a beautiful young woman is found in a stolen Ferrari, the investigation leads to a family of car thieves.
episodes.title: Cavallino Rampante

episodes.synopsis: A night out for a friendly drink takes a very unexpected turn when Danny and his rookie cops are caught up in a shooting.
episodes.title: Officer Involved

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team investigates when the recently paroled brother of a young basketball prodigy is implicated in a murder.
episodes.title: Air Apparent

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate when a fraternity prank goes awry on Halloween and a pledge master is left for dead in an open grave.
episodes.title: Get Me Out Of Here!

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate when news of a high school house party goes viral, resulting in overcrowding, a collapsed porch and a teenage girl's death.
episodes.title: Crushed

episodes.title: Crossroads

episodes.title: Means To An End

episodes.title: Who's There?

episodes.title: Kill Screen

episodes.title: Flash Pop

episodes.title: Slainte

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs are called to a Brooklyn housing project to investigate the murder of a successful businessman who felt the pull of his old neighborhood.
episodes.title: Unwrapped

episodes.synopsis: When Mac is shot, he finds himself in limbo between life and death, as he fights for his life, it's up to his team to bring the shooter to justice.
episodes.title: Near Death

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate when a fire chief - a friend of Mac's - is killed in a blaze that used the same technique as a recently paroled arsonist.
episodes.title: Reignited

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team rushes to stop serial arsonist Leonard Brooks after he begins using fire against people from his dark past.
episodes.title: Where There's Smoke..

episodes.title: 2,918 Miles

episodes.synopsis: The CSI New York team of investigators race to catch a shooter when Lindsay is injured during the attempted murder of a political candidate.

episodes.title: Misconceptions

episodes.synopsis: The CSIs investigate a twisted fairy tale when a woman in a ball gown is found at the bottom of the pond outside Belvedere Castle in Central Park.
episodes.title: The Lady In The Lake

episodes.synopsis: When a psychiatrist's patients are being systematically murdered, the CSIs are forced to play along in a game of Clue in order to catch the killer.
episodes.title: Clue: Si

episodes.title: Late Admissions

episodes.synopsis: When Det. Lovato's cover is inadvertently blown, the CSI's investigate the Latin street gang she infiltrated when undercover.
episodes.title: Blood Out

episodes.title: Command+P

episodes.title: Seth And Apep

episodes.synopsis: On Valentine's Day, Detective Mac Taylor and the rest of the CSI New York team tackle three twisted tales of love gone wrong.
episodes.title: Blood Actually

episodes.synopsis: Community unrest over the police shooting of an unarmed man forces Mac and the CSI New York team to move quickly to solve the case.
episodes.title: Today Is Life
